	<content><![CDATA[const reverseString = str => [...str].reverse().join('');]]></content>
	<description>Reverses a string.  Use the spread operator (`...`) and `Array.reverse()` to reverse the order of the characters in the string. Combine characters to get a string using `String.join('')`.</description>
